com.bugsnag.android

Interface SessionTrackingApiClient


  • public interface SessionTrackingApiClient
    Posts an array of sessions to the Bugsnag Session Tracking API. Custom implementations of this client can be used in place of the default implementation, by calling Bugsnag.setSessionTrackingApiClient(SessionTrackingApiClient)
    See Also:
    DefaultHttpClient
